data.description: Gorgeous lagoon view at the end of a cul-de-sac, on one of the arguable best homesites in Coosaw Point on Lady's Island. Beautiful custom home has been meticulously maintained w/ space for entertaining, 4 BD/3 BTH, 2-car detached garage structurally built to have a carriage house added in the future. Completely turnkey w/ chef's kitchen, great rm, main floor primary w/ huge BTH + 2nd BD & BTH on main. Lagoon view of screened in back porch is a dream! Loads of upgrades, millwork, gas FP, true southern front porch w/loads of natural lightwhy wait to build when you can move right in! New AC/ducting & new roof will be installed in next 2 weeks 2023-11-06
